survived the ship going down? OH where are they?" She put her paws up 
on hte side of the rim, her head barely poking over the side of the 
pod. "MOM! DAD! WHERE ARE YOU? I"m here mom, over....here" She got a 
glimse of that was left of the ship.  She looked as saw a bot arm 
laying there.  Glancing over more, she saw scrap metel stretching for 
a long ways out. She steps down and lowered her head. "They didn't 
make it, did they?"
